{"tid":87772,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯去季掙近60億　破皇馬11年壟斷　膺全球最高收入球會","createTime":"2017-01-20T05:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T12:15:44.000Z","uid":74164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1763f4d750f8bad130caee38f0ff3797ba1724ac","tid":87772,"uid":74164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里不敵曼聯？德勤公布上季球會收入排行榜，近年戰績欠佳的英超球會曼聯，受惠英超轉播費大增，2015/16球季錄得創球會紀錄的6.89億歐元（約57億港元）收入，取代雄霸榜首11年的皇馬，重新成為全球收入最多的球會。<br />\n<br />\n英超轉播費成關鍵<br />\n根據四大國際會計師事務所之一德勤會計師事務所公布，英超曼聯於2015/16球季，商業收入增長1億歐元（約8.3億港元），總收入更錄得6.89億歐元打破球會紀錄。事實上，雖然曼聯近年戰績不佳，但由於球隊上季重返歐聯，得到歐聯轉播收益，加上與adidas的新贊助合約生效，以及受惠英超轉播費大增，令其收入不跌反升。曼聯更超越「西甲雙雄」巴塞隆拿和皇家馬德里，由前季的第3一舉升上第一，自2003/04年球季後再度榮登全球最賺錢球會。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c646851a091873a96dbb53bd36728a2966c5d7","tid":87772,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"曼連<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805c4d9991c41067de8878de5100f5cb7fd33b6b","tid":87772,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:01:50.000Z","msg":"60億可以買60個妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9dceecf6240a9002df245fdb0867ab8e90ade7","tid":87772,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:59:26.000Z","msg":"買晒美斯C朗大聖爺都仲得"},{"pid":"23d20a11a85b00da2aa3d5d5372950a47081bb12","tid":87772,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfcb977e7c4dd85c1e599e62b0b6c2dcf491a840","tid":87772,"uid":169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim